"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-05-27-Olympics-Chinese-women-s-sprint-team-gears-up-for-Paris-Games-1tWyfNkTH5S-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  China's women's sprint cycling team are hoping to make it two gold medals in as many Olympic Games when they arrive in Paris.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999441120791781, \"rank\": 5.014654464149073e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997316049662, \"rank\": 2.6839503356831446e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Tokyo Olympic Games, Bao Shanju and Zhong Tianshi won gold in a time of 31.895 seconds after the pair broke the world record in qualifying with a time of 31.804 seconds.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bao_Shanju\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bao Shanju\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bao_Shanju\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bao_Shanju\"}, {\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhong_Tianshi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhong Tianshi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhong_Tianshi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhong_Tianshi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, Bao is joined by Guo Yufang and Yuan Liying because the event will include three riders for the first time.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renminbi\", \"score\": 0.7624561715893541, \"rank\": 0.30697229487913036, \"text\": \"Yuan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renminbi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renminbi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guo will race in the first lap and Yuan, the youngest, will go last.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renminbi\", \"score\": 0.7624561715893541, \"rank\": 0.30697229487913036, \"text\": \"Yuan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renminbi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renminbi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old Bao, having won gold in Tokyo three years ago, is the most experienced rider and understands the pressure that comes with being an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 753, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8949735376201856, \"rank\": 0.11723618409148939, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Tokyo Olympic Games was one of the most important competitions I had competed in,\\\" said Bao, Tokyo Olympics team sprint gold medalist.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Prior to the Tokyo Games, I had never been to a world championships or an Asia championships, only the world cup.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was so nervous before the Games that I would dream of competing with Germany while I was sleeping,\\\" Bao said.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8469837919788287, \"rank\": 0.1760781454900607, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After topping the podium in Tokyo, I became even more anxious when competing because I felt the burden of being an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8949735376201856, \"rank\": 0.11723618409148939, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was afraid of making mistakes or losing to opponents who are younger than me.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I put a lot of pressure on myself at that time,\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the most important thing for three of us now is to win a race, and that will greatly boost my confidence,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Cover: Bao Shanju of China.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bao_Shanju\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bao Shanju\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bao_Shanju\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bao_Shanju\"}, {\"begin\":